---
[v2] net: ethernet: mtk_eth_soc: add extended MIB counters for NETSYSv3

Without this patch, the users are unable to obtain ethtool statistic
data for the Unicast, Multicast, and Broadcast counters from both the
GMAC and XGMAC.
---
v2: Fix out-of-bounds access issue on MT7988's eth0.
v1: Add extended MIB counters for NETSYSv3.
---

From b1b27f32994b0f0266844df4a0b42b77c4ab230b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Bo-Cun Chen <bc-bocun.chen@mediatek.com>
Date: Wed, 22 Apr 2026 12:47:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] net: ethernet: mtk_eth_soc: add extended MIB counters for
 NETSYSv3

Without this patch, the users are unable to read ethtool statistic data
for the Unicast, Multicast, and Broadcast counters from both the GMAC
and XGMAC.

Signed-off-by: Bo-Cun Chen <bc-bocun.chen@mediatek.com>
